title: Spooky
summary: The ghost of the haunted house comes at night.
developerAddress: House # 616, Street # 69, Sector I-8/3, Islamabad, Pakistan.
description: The ghost of the haunted house comes at night. Bring the spooky and thriller watch face for your android wear. The illustration design is used and there are many funky color themes which can be change according to your mood.  This watch face has digital time and funky font is used for the display of the time. When the watch is not in use the watch face goes into ambient mode which save the battery just by showing the time.
